name: AISeller
abi: event OnSell(uint256 orderid, address buyer, uint256 goodid, uint256 price)
event RoleAdminChanged(bytes32 indexed role, bytes32 indexed previousAdminRole, bytes32 indexed newAdminRole)
event RoleGranted(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
event RoleRevoked(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
function Admin_SetSellInfo(uint256 id, tuple(uint256 id, uint256 price) info)
function GetOrders(uint256 index, uint256 count) view returns (tuple(address buyer, uint256 orderid, uint256 goodid, uint256 price, uint256 time)[])
function GetSellInfo(uint256 id) view returns (tuple(uint256 id, uint256 price) info)
function hasRole(bytes32 role, address account) view returns (bool)
function orders(uint256) view returns (address buyer, uint256 orderid, uint256 goodid, uint256 price, uint256 time)
function sellinfos(uint256) view returns (uint256 id, uint256 price)
